atic quarrel the two young teens had when they were dating. Upon making up, they each tattooed the message as a reminder of how horrible it was being apart. She never imagined the tattoo would take on such poignant meaning years later. 2014."},"credit":"Tanya Habjouqa","image_crops":{"superJumbo":{"height":1365,"width":2048,"url":"https:\/\/static01.nyt.com\/images\/2014\/10\/28\/blogs\/20141028-lens-tanya-slide-NNVU\/20141028-lens-tanya-slide-NNVU-superJumbo.jpg"}},"url":"\/slideshow\/2014\/10\/28\/blogs\/20141028-lens-tanya\/s\/null.html","short_url":"http:\/\/nyti.ms\/2b4pM3K","approved_for_syndication":false},{"data_id":100000003202083,"slide_url":"20141028-lens-tanya-slide-W18T","image_type":"photo","caption":{"full":"<p>F, 35, had little room in her Peugeot as she fled Daraa with her five children after her husband was killed. She filmed a video of her home in case she never saw it again. She took this wooden tray her husband had bought her on a trip to Beirut. 2014.<\/p>","short":"&#8220;F&#8221;, 35, had little room in her Peugeot as she fled Deraa with her five children after her fighter husband was killed. She filmed a mobile video of her home in case she never saw it again. She took this wooden tray her husband had bought her on a trip to Beirut. 2014."},"credit":"Tanya Habjouqa","image_crops":{"superJumbo":{"height":1365,"width":2048,"url":"https:\/\/static01.nyt.com\/images\/2014\/10\/28\/blogs\/20141028-lens-tanya-slide-W18T\/20141028-lens-tanya-slide-W18T-superJumbo.jpg"}},"url":"\/slideshow\/2014\/10\/28\/blogs\/20141028-lens-tanya\/s\/null.html","short_url":"http:\/\/nyti.ms\/2b4pM3K","approved_for_syndication":false}]},"related_assets":[]}	</script>
	
